column5: Hi Guys,  Used to be able to search the site with the search button down at the bottom of the page. It is know longer there?
Look up, look waaaay up!! Beside your profile and sign out links on the right.

On my screen, the word "search" is barely visible in the box and I didn't know where it was either until I just went looking for it after reading this post.  Everything else is very visible on the pages, except for that one word so perhaps that's what the problem is.
